Thank you for this component - I'm contributing this to help as my HA shows various fields with no data. The car is built between 07-2013 and 10-2015 which used to be important for a BMW labs Widget to talk to IFTTT. (That is another story of course but it does imply that the car is not so dumb.)

Using a BMW CD app I can remotely lock / unlock / flash / sound horn / locate the car in the airport car park so the question is what magic does the app use? I can say that those empty HA BMW component fields (that is fuel, range & miles travelled) DO show data in the BMW app when you're USB connected to the car.

